# Plugin manifests are formatted by scripts/bump-version.sh (sed-based,
# inline arrays preserved). Prettier's JSON formatter expands inline
# arrays to multi-line and removes trailing newlines, which:
#   1. Churns the diff on every version bump
#   2. Has caused Cowork/Claude Code plugin manifest parser failures
#      (v0.1.4 install was broken until format was restored)
# Keep these files out of Prettier's reach.
.claude-plugin/plugin.json
.claude-plugin/marketplace.json
hooks/hooks.json

# Skill descriptions need to be inspectable as raw text (1024-char
# Anthropic skill description limit means precise length awareness
# matters — see v0.1.3 release notes).
skills/**/SKILL.md
